            . After he and my husband were gone to the Half Moon, he came up and told me my husband was very angry with me, and would murder me; to which I gave but little heed; and in that time he had took out the drawer, and taken the two rings out. I was a washing, with my back towards him. When we took him, he confessed it to me and others, but denied it before the Justice.</p>
